{"id:": "/div[1]", "tag": "div", "attributes": {"type": "article", "{http://www.w3.org/XML/1998/namespace}id": "MG-1698-05_077", "resp": "wordpro"}, "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/head[1]", "tag": "head", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/head[1]/text()[1]", "text": "[Satyre sur la Conversation]"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]", "tag": "bibl", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]/title[1]", "tag": "title", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]/title[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Mercure galant"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]/text()[1]", "text": ", mai 1698 [tome 5], p. 77-85."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[1]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Il n’y a rien de plus agréable que la conversation, mais pour y estre reçû avec plaisir il faut s’examiner avec soin, & voir si l’on n’a point les défauts dont il est parlé dans la Satyre que je vous envoye. Elle est de M"}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[1]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[1]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "r"}], "attributes": {"rend": "sup"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[1]/text()[2]", "text": " Hebert de Château-Thierry."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]", "tag": "quote", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/label[1]", "tag": "label", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/label[1]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/label[1]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "À Madame de"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/label[1]/text()[1]", "text": " ***."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]", "tag": "lg", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[1]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[1]/text()[1]", "text": "La Conversation est un commerce aimable,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[2]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[2]/text()[1]", "text": "Quand joignant comme vous l’utile à l’agréable,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[3]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[3]/text()[1]", "text": "On connoît ce qu’on vaut sans trop de vanité,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[4]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[4]/text()[1]", "text": "Et qu’on montre par tout de la docilité."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[5]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[5]/text()[1]", "text": "Mais je ne puis souffrir ces gens dont l’ignorance"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[6]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[6]/text()[1]", "text": "N’a pour le soûtenir qu’une sorte arrogance,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[7]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[7]/text()[1]", "text": "Et qu’on voit tous les jours faire les connoisseurs,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[8]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[8]/text()[1]", "text": "Décider hardiment, s’ériger en Censeurs,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[9]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[9]/text()[1]", "text": "En un mot s’aveuglant d’une vaine manie"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[10]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[10]/text()[1]", "text": "Pretendre que tout cede à leur foible genie."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[11]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[11]/text()[1]", "text": "La dispute contr’eux n’est jamais de saison,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[12]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[12]/text()[1]", "text": "Ne les pas applaudir c’est choquer la raison ;"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[13]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[13]/text()[1]", "text": "Ils pensent avoir seuls le bons sens en partage,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[14]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[14]/text()[1]", "text": "Mécontens d’un chacun, ennemis de l’usage"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[15]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[15]/text()[1]", "text": "Sans cesse on les entend contredire & blâmer,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[16]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[16]/text()[1]", "text": "Ils sont piquans, chagrins, prests à tout reformer."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[17]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[17]/text()[1]", "text": "Prétend-t-on par hazard entâmer une histoire,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[18]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[18]/text()[1]", "text": "Ils en sont seuls instruits, si l’on veut les en croire,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[19]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[19]/text()[1]", "text": "Quelque démangeaison qu’on ait de la conter,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[20]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[20]/text()[1]", "text": "Ils prennent la parole, il les faut écouter ;"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[21]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[21]/text()[1]", "text": "Pour débiter des riens ils imposent silence,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[22]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[22]/text()[1]", "text": "Et des plus modérez lassent la patience."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[23]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[23]/text()[1]", "text": "Ils parlent brusquement ; on diroit à leur ton"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[24]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[24]/text()[1]", "text": "Que ce sont des Docteurs qui nous font la leçon."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[25]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[25]/text()[1]", "text": " D’autre part un Sçavant qui croit que l’art de plaire"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[26]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[26]/text()[1]", "text": "Est de toûjours briller, & jamais ne se taire,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[27]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[27]/text()[1]", "text": "Oubliant de répondre aux choses qu’on luy dit,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[28]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[28]/text()[1]", "text": "Ne songe tout au plus qu’à montrer de l’esprit."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[29]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[29]/text()[1]", "text": "Impatient d’abord de le faire connoistre,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[30]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[30]/text()[1]", "text": "Il ôte le plaisir aux autres de paroistre,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[31]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[31]/text()[1]", "text": "Et fatiguant chacun par ses beaux sentimens,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[32]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[32]/text()[1]", "text": "Perd le fruit attendu de ses raisonnemens,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[33]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[33]/text()[1]", "text": "Car pour estre goûté, la plus sûre maxime"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[34]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[34]/text()[1]", "text": "N’est pas par ses discours de briguer de l’estime,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[35]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[35]/text()[1]", "text": "N’est pas tant de donner du lustre à ce qu’on dit,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[36]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[36]/text()[1]", "text": "Que de faire trouver aux autres de l’esprit."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[37]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[37]/text()[1]", "text": " Un Puriste d’ailleurs, esclave de l’usage,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[38]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[38]/text()[1]", "text": "Ne produit rien d’heureux par son fade langage."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[39]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[39]/text()[1]", "text": "Il ne risqueroit pas la moindre expression,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[40]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[40]/text()[1]", "text": "Deust-elle estre l’objet de l’admiration."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[41]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[41]/text()[1]", "text": "Il parle proprement, mais à chaque parole"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[42]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[42]/text()[1]", "text": "Sa morne attention déconcerte & désole ;"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[43]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[43]/text()[1]", "text": "Et pour affecter trop la régularité,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[44]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[44]/text()[1]", "text": "Il rebute chacun par sa sterilité."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[45]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[45]/text()[1]", "text": " Un diseur de Phebus dédaignant le vulgaire"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[46]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[46]/text()[1]", "text": "Fait prendre à son genie un essor témeraire."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[47]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[47]/text()[1]", "text": "S’imaginant parler le langage des Dieux,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[48]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[48]/text()[1]", "text": "De sens froid il débite un fatras ennuïeux"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[49]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[49]/text()[1]", "text": "De grands mots assommans, d’épitetes forcées,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[50]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[50]/text()[1]", "text": "Un galimatias de phrases entassées,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[51]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[51]/text()[1]", "text": "Et de tout son beau dire unique Admirateur,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[52]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[52]/text()[1]", "text": "S’acquiert la qualité d’impertinent Parleur."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[53]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[53]/text()[1]", "text": "On ne parle en effet que pour se faire entendre."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[54]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[54]/text()[1]", "text": "À quoy sert un beau mot que l’on ne peut comprendre ?"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[55]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[55]/text()[1]", "text": "Il est d’autres défauts, dont l’incongruité"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[56]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[56]/text()[1]", "text": "Ne dégoûte pas moins de la société."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[57]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[57]/text()[1]", "text": " J’aperçois Philemon qui brusquement approche,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[58]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[58]/text()[1]", "text": "Et porte le bon sens, & la raison en poche,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[59]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[59]/text()[1]", "text": "Car à peine entre-t-il en conversation,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[60]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[60]/text()[1]", "text": "Qu’il veut que l’on défere à son opinion,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[61]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[61]/text()[1]", "text": "Et pour tout fondement il parie, il assure."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[62]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[62]/text()[1]", "text": "Pour peu que l’on conteste, il se tourmente, il jure,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[63]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[63]/text()[1]", "text": "Vingt Loüis bien comptez sont toutes ses raisons."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[64]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[64]/text()[1]", "text": " Le fâcheux Dorilas fait des comparaisons,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[65]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[65]/text()[1]", "text": "Qui choquent le bon sens, les mœurs, la bien-séance."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[66]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[66]/text()[1]", "text": "Il ne sçait point avoir d’égard, de déference ;"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[67]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[67]/text()[1]", "text": "Il est désobligeant, satirique, indiscret ;"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[68]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[68]/text()[1]", "text": "À peine parle-t-il que chacun a son fait :"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[69]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[69]/text()[1]", "text": " Ariste est à l’affust de la moindre parole,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[70]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[70]/text()[1]", "text": "Rire, turlupiner, badiner c’est son rôle,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[71]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[71]/text()[1]", "text": "Il croit trouver par tout de la subtilité,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[72]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[72]/text()[1]", "text": "Et pas un mot n’échappe à sa vivacité ;"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[73]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[73]/text()[1]", "text": "Mais de ce bel esprit la plus grande finesse"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[74]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[74]/text()[1]", "text": "N’est que fatuité, fausse délicatesse,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[75]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[75]/text()[1]", "text": "Qu’on aperçoit d’abord, & quelque fois on rit"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[76]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[76]/text()[1]", "text": "De la pointe, & souvent d’Ariste qui la dit."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[77]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[77]/text()[1]", "text": " L’insolent Antiphon parle avec non-chalance."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[78]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[78]/text()[1]", "text": "Il est reveur, abstrait, amateur du silence."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[79]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[79]/text()[1]", "text": "Avec tout son esprit il n’a point d’agrément,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[80]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[80]/text()[1]", "text": "Et n’écoutant pas bien il répond sottement."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[81]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[81]/text()[1]", "text": " Le sterile Cleon pour toute gentillesse,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[82]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[82]/text()[1]", "text": "Pour tout fond, ne fait voir qu’un peu de politesse,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[83]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[83]/text()[1]", "text": "En termes different repete ce qu’on dit."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[84]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[84]/text()[1]", "text": "Sourit à tous momens, & sans cesse applaudit."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[85]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[85]/text()[1]", "text": " Mais je voudrois en vain par ma foible censure,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[86]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[86]/text()[1]", "text": "Reformer les défauts dont je fais la peinture."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[87]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[87]/text()[1]", "text": "C’est de vous qu’on attend cet important effet,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[88]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[88]/text()[1]", "text": "Vous estes en cet Art un modele parfait."}]}]}]}]}